  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate the contribution of PET-CT with F18-choline in the
      diagnosis of thyroid nodule with indeterminate cytology in order to guide the best indication
      of surgical resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
